    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce mandatory licensing and regulation of animal rescue centres",
        "additional_details": "We believe current arrangements do not adequately ensure the welfare of animals at animal rescue centres, or prevent dogs being rehomed when they already have an owner.",
        "background": "We want all animal rescue centres to be required to apply for a licence, and subject to regulation requiring regular inspections and checks of animals in their care, to check history, potential theft issues, etc.",
